+dnl This is the newlib/libc/sys/d10v configure.in file.
+dnl Process this file with autoconf to produce a configure script.
+
+AC_PREREQ(2.5)
+AC_INIT(creat.c)
+
+dnl Can't be done in NEWLIB_CONFIGURE because that confuses automake. 
